<div></div>
<div class="row">
    <div class=" col-lg-3"></div>
    <div class=" col-lg-6">
        <form action="/sendinviting" method="POST">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="name">Your first and last name:</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" name="name">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="friend_name">First name of your friend:</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" name="name">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Email address of your friend:</label>
            <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="email">
          </div>
          We will send an e-mail to your friend inviting him/her to join FileIrsfForms. After they sign up you will recive a bonus to submit one form for free.
          <br/>
          <br/>
          <%= hidden_field_tag :authenticity_token, form_authenticity_token -%>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Send</button>
        </form>
    </div>
    <div class=" col-lg-3"></div>
</div>